name: consciously caught in darkness
description:
Holders of this token will become living entities of this tenebrous algosystem. They will try to stay together, after all darkness is less scary when experienced together. You may want to help them but, beware, to them you may just be another horrific keeper of the dark. You might shine light but what is it in the eyes of those who can no longer see it ?

A tokenized piece. It may break in the future if the hicdex api were to change.
controls: stuff with mouse
Inspired by the work of Kim Asendorf
